---
model: "gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview" 
input:
  schema:
    inline_images?(array, inline image data):
      type: object
      properties:
        mime_type: string
        contents: string
    modification_prompt: string
---
{{role "user"}}
Modify the following reference image strictly based on these instructions:
{{modification_prompt}}

{{#each inline_images}}
  {{media type=mime_type data=contents}}
{{/each}}